title: Thomas Newman - Less Than Zero Original Score (Remastered)
description:
Less Than Zero Score (Original Score)

Composer: Thomas Newman
Bitrate: 320kbps

Despite the official score being unreleased, I have obtained these tracks from an unnamed source. Originally, the quality was sub-par with the tracks containing hiss, hum, clicks and pops; from which I assume originated from the recording source. I have done my best to recover the beauty of these with my own re-mastering.


The following is the track listing with unofficial titles:

01. Early Phone Call
02. Feeling Nostalgic
03. Zuma Beach
04. I Need $50,000
05. Sex At The Loft
06. Blair And Her Dad
07. Julian On The Stairs
08. Going Through Withdrawal
09. Heading To Palm Springs
10. Rip's Hotel Suite
11. The Cemetery (Extended)
12. Quick Escape
13. Seeing Blair Again
14. The Loft's Been Trashed
15. Julian's Dead
